# SDLC Agêntico Version
version: "2.0.4"
build_date: "2026-01-24"
release_notes: |
  sdlc-import v2.1.0 - Advanced Analysis & Testing

  Features:
  - feat(sdlc-import): ADR Validator - Valida LGPD, RLS, JWT, multi-tenancy patterns
  - feat(sdlc-import): Graph Generator - Cria knowledge graph com relações semânticas
  - feat(sdlc-import): Issue Creator - Cria issues no GitHub a partir de análise
  - feat(sdlc-import): Migration Analyzer - Analisa EF Core, Alembic, Flyway migrations
  - feat(sdlc-import): Graph integrity quality gate (graph-integrity.yml)
  - feat(sdlc-import): ADR validation rules (adr_validation_rules.yml)
  - feat(sdlc-import): Migration patterns detection (migration_patterns.yml)

  Testing:
  - test(sdlc-import): 306 testes ADRValidator (LGPD, RLS, JWT, multi-tenancy)
  - test(sdlc-import): 234 testes GraphGenerator (structure, concepts, adjacency)
  - test(sdlc-import): 184 testes IssueCreator (priority, GitHub CLI, formatting)
  - test(sdlc-import): 275 testes MigrationAnalyzer (EF Core, Alembic, Flyway)
  - test(sdlc-import): Total 999 novos testes unitários (+2844 linhas)

  Impact:
  - Validação automática de ADRs contra boas práticas (LGPD, segurança)
  - Knowledge graph gerado automaticamente do código
  - Issues criados automaticamente no GitHub Projects
  - Migrations analisadas para detectar patterns e tech debt

